William Smith died four months after his mother Alison Overton lost her battle with leukaemia . 
  The teenager from Grimsby wanted to remind himself of his mother following her death . 
  He wore her bandana and sprayed her perfume around the house after she died . 
  He hanged himself in August last year and was discovered by his grandmother . 
  Inquest heard he had 'settled back in well' at school following his mother's death . 
